PWAS.Model.User

PWAS.Model.User Class Reference

Partial class that implements partial method OnCreated() to take care of fields that have default values in the database schema. Linq-to-SQL does not properly take care of default values, so these have to be set explicitly if someone creates a User without assigning a value to these fields. More...

Detailed Description

Partial class that implements partial method OnCreated() to take care of fields that have default values in the database schema. Linq-to-SQL does not properly take care of default values, so these have to be set explicitly if someone creates a User without assigning a value to these fields.
